description: Utility class for serializing and deserializing Note objects to and from JSON strings.

classes.name: NoteJson
classes.description: Provides static methods to encode and decode Note objects and collections to/from JSON strings.

methods.name: encodeNote
methods.description: Converts a Note object into a JSON string.

methods.name: decodeNote
methods.description: Creates a Note object from a JSON string.

methods.name: encodeNotes
methods.description: Converts a list of Note objects into a JSON string.

methods.name: decodeNotes
methods.description: Creates a list of Note objects from a JSON string.
